STATE of North Carolina
v.
Kenneth Delano BOBBITT. No. 667P03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 4, 2004. Kenneth Delano Bobbitt, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Tom Horner, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by-Defendant on the 22nd day of December 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th day of March 2004."
